    • updateItem

      public void updateItem(Variable variable, boolean empty)
      update l'affichage et l'item de la cellule selon la variables reçue en argument.
      Overrides:
      updateItem in class Cell<Variable>
      Parameters:
      variable - The new item for the cell.
      empty - whether or not this cell represents data from the list. If it is empty, then it does not represent any domain data, but is a cell being used to render an "empty" row.
